imgui >= 1.80
	https://github.com/ocornut/imgui
	clone depot here
	checkout c6e0284ac58b3f205c95365478888f7b53b077e2
	apply patch "external/imgui_imconfig.h.patch" to "external/imgui/imconfig.h"

imgui-sfml == 2.5
	https://github.com/eliasdaler/imgui-sfml
	clone depot here
	checkout 9cc8c57a4565551087be0d9aeb3ae55490aa1207

implot
	https://github.com/epezent/implot.git
	clone depot here

SFML >= 2.5.0
	use apt-get install libsfml-dev if you can and CHECK VERSION
	if you can't :
		https://github.com/SFML/SFML
		https://www.sfml-dev.org/download/sfml/2.5.1/index-fr.php
		Edit Makefile accordingly

PerlinNoise >= 3.0
	https://github.com/Reputeless/PerlinNoise
	clone depot here


lucky set-up :

sudo apt-get install libsfml-dev
git clone https://github.com/ocornut/imgui.git
git clone https://github.com/eliasdaler/imgui-sfml.git
git clone https://github.com/epezent/implot.git
git clone https://github.com/Reputeless/PerlinNoise.git

apply patch "external/imgui_imconfig.h.patch" to "external/imgui/imconfig.h"

Execute make in the folder test and execute imgui.out
